{"id":1765,"date":"2024-09-14T19:49:49","date_gmt":"2024-09-14T19:49:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1765"},"modified":"2024-09-18T23:26:01","modified_gmt":"2024-09-18T23:26:01","slug":"metagrossite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/","title":{"rendered":"Metagrossite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Metagrossite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>\n        If starter is Beldum: Find the stone in the Shadow Base Warehouse in Frozen Heights. It&#8217;s behind a locked door that you need the level 2 Key Pass to unlock.<br \/>\n        <br \/>\n        Otherwise: It is a gift from Professor Log after completing the \u201cPortal Purge\u201d post-game mission.\n      <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Metagross<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat Shadow Boss Zeff at the Shadow Base<\/li>\n<li>Complete the main story<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Acquiring the Metagrossite depends on whether you chose Beldum as your starter.<\/p>\n<h3>If Beldum Was Your Starter<\/h3>\n<p>Fly to your house at Frozen Heights and head west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-players-house-at-frozen-heights.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly come across a frozen lake that you want to follow north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-frozen-lake-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the frozen lake north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the frozen lake north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see the Shadow Base entrance you want to go through in the lake\u2019s northwest corner.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-shadow-base.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Shadow Base. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Shadow Base.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Now, follow the path west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/04-pokemon-unbound-going-west-after-entering-the-warehouse.jpg\" alt=\"Going west after entering the warehouse. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going west after entering the warehouse.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the room at the end of the path to reach the area where you started the game.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/05-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-west-room.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the west room. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the west room.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Metagrossite is behind a locked door to the west that requires the level 2 Key Pass acquired during the main story.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/metagrossite\/06-pokemon-unbound-acquiring-the-metagrossite-from-behind-the-locked-door.jpg\" alt=\"Acquiring the Metagrossite from behind the locked door. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Acquiring the Metagrossite from behind the locked door.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3>If Beldum Wasn\u2019t Your Starter<\/h3>\n<p>If Beldum wasn\u2019t your starter, you can acquire the Metagrossite by completing the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-050\/\">\u201cPortal Purge\u201d<\/a> post-game mission the professor gives you after you complete the game.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1766,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1765","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1765","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1766"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1765"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1765"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":